with saddles to His Majesty...

646
00:50:09,340 --> 00:50:10,679
and asked for me.

647
00:50:12,250 --> 00:50:14,050
He was a prince of Chahar.

648
00:50:14,780 --> 00:50:17,820
When His Majesty was conquering Chahar,

649
00:50:17,949 --> 00:50:20,460
