to take me with him.

652
00:50:29,599 --> 00:50:31,329
I trusted him.

653
00:50:33,300 --> 00:50:35,400
But he did not come back for years.

654
00:50:37,440 --> 00:50:39,340
For the daughters of emperors,

655
00:50:39,340 --> 00:50:41,710
