684
00:53:14,530 --> 00:53:18,570
Even if I marry another man in the future,

685
00:53:19,230 --> 00:53:21,170
I will take you with me.

686
00:53:25,369 --> 00:53:27,409
So, tonight, you must...

687
00:53:37,449 --> 00:53:39,420
serve me...

688
