693
00:55:09,639 --> 00:55:10,949
Last night, did we perhaps...

694
00:55:13,380 --> 00:55:14,820
I mean, you and I...

695
00:55:17,320 --> 00:55:19,750
Do not worry. Nothing happened.

696
00:55:31,570 --> 00:55:33,300
